KNIGHT et al. v. LUTCHER & MOORE LUMBER CO. et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. October 14, 1905.) No. 1,401. In Error to the .Circuit Court of the United States for the Western District of Louisiana. For former opinion, see 136 Fed. 404.

Before PARDEE, McCORMICK, and SHELBY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

No one of the judges who participated in the decision of this ease having asked for a rehearing, and being still satisfied our former decision is correct, the rehearing herein applied for is denied.
